1.1
log
@Moved these tests here from sbin/isakmpd/regress.  They mostly work
but are not enabled by default yet.
@
text
@#	$OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.14 2003/06/03 14:39:51 ho Exp $
#	$EOM: Makefile,v 1.16 2000/09/28 12:53:27 niklas Exp $

